text: Megan Fox may have just celebrated seven years of marriage with her husband Brian Austin Green, but she’s still seriously smitten with her man! The actress, 31, took to Instagram to share a throwback pic of Brian, 44, taken during his 90210 days. In the caption, she thanked Brian for donating his “heartthrob” DNA to their three sons, Noah, Bodhi, and Journey. Click through to see Megan’s hilarious (and hot!) tribute to her good-looking husband!
title: Megan Fox Thanks Hot Hubby Brian Austin Green For Passing On His ‘Heartthrob’ DNA
